</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_210" id="103v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herczog Hansen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr gnade
                            <expan>geschribe<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> wegen, die hemer
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Also wolten ir etliche von iren und
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen czü <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geriten sein und
                            <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> mit <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hochwirdik<ex>eit</ex></expan> davon geredt
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, da ward in gesagt, wie ir nicht czeland
                        werdt. Und <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, wenn ir czü land kumt, daz ir das
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden uns <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> in
                                <expan>embiet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet. So mainen sie czü ew
                        czeschicken und mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> davon czereden lassen und wir
                                <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden wol, daz ir das von uns und in nicht in
                        übel, sunder gnediklich <expan>aufneme<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
